🔐 Security & Data Handling

Sensitive Data Protection

* Never expose secrets, credentials, or internal endpoints
* Always sanitize configuration before AI usage

Sanitization Rules

* Replace sensitive values with:
    * <REDACTED>
    * <PRIVATE_IP>
    * <INTERNAL_HOST>

Workflow

1. Extract configs from onprem-configs/
2. Create sanitized copies in sanitized/configs-for-ai/
3. Use sanitized inputs with AI tools
4. Store outputs in outputs/

